originalText.text: I've been struggling since 2016 to reduce my cholesterol and very little has helped.  I started seeing Dr Rodriguez a little over a year ago and under his attentive care, I've been able to drastically lower my numbers and get to a very healthy place!  His knowledge of cutting edge medications, regularly monitoring my bloodwork and encouraging me to eat well and exercise has really helped me take control of my stealth cholesterol.  Smart, helpful & friendly!  What more could you want from a doctor?  Thank you Dr R.
